<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index/style_index_announce.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
<% if (user && user.role === 'S') { %>
    <%- include('../partials/user_partials/nav_senior') %>

<% } else { %>
    <%- include('../partials/user_partials/nav_index') %>
    <%}%>

  <div class="about-header">
    <div class="about-header__inner">
      <p class="section-tag">공지 사항</p>
      <h1 class="about-header__title">새로운 소식을 전해드립니다</h1>
      <p class="about-header__sub">서비스 업데이트, 점검 안내, 이용 정책 변경 등 중요한 내용을 확인하세요.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br><br><br>
  

  

  <div class="notice-list">

<% notices.forEach(function(notice, index) { %>
<div class="notice-item" data-id="<%= index %>" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
  

  <div class="notice-view-mode" style="display: flex; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
    <div class="notice-content">
      <span class="notice-badge <%= notice.isNew ? 'new' : '' %> notice-badge-text"><%= notice.category %></span>
  <a href="/user/user_service/user_announce"
     class="notice-link"
     style="margin-left:10px;">
    <span class="notice-title-text"><%= notice.title %></span>
  </a>
      <span class="notice-date" style="margin-left: 10px; color: #888;"><%= notice.date %></span>
    </div>
  </div>


</div>
<% }); %>
</main>


</div> </main> <div class="clearfix-padding"></div>





<footer class="footer">
  © 2025 <span>복약안심서비스</span> | Team Jetson5 | 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼
</footer>
</body>
